Now we can point to any file containing all dependencies to install
along with hashes. This will only work with hashes available for all
the dependencies. The file name can be anything.

Example of building such a requirements file using pip-tools

pip-compile --generate-hashes --allow-unsafe \
  --output-file=requirements.txt requirements.in
